{"tid":1764101,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"窮則變，變則通，行翻百分百的和理非一路有何不可？","createTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T05:32:01.000Z","uid":28645,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c60fad2333c425c49c068c090b1317fc1233f80","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"唔係要割同指責，只不過係覺得勇武貌似已經去到一個盡頭。你當我左膠，但唔想再見到前線嘅勇武再因為唔對等嘅武力而被出事...<br />\n<br />\n或者可參考下波蘭嘅舊路？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E9%8C%84-%E5%85%AD-%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%258C%2584-%25E5%2585%25AD-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=88c5264d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2594%259F%25E9%258C%2584-%25E5%2585%25AD-%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2595%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%2F&h=8cab060c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E9%8C%84-%E5%85%AD-%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</a><br />\n<br />\n用和平嘅模式去進行持續性嘅抗爭，唔可以因為見到前線好慘，因為有悲慘畫面，先被感動同道德感召而行出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n正如罷工一樣，非自願無工會領頭嘅罷工係無意義，政府只會射個波俾示威者去減少對其威權產生嘅傷害。<br />\n<br />\n已被改變嘅係信念，但要再改變嘅係行動。當大罷工連線果邊嘅組織成熟之後，喺合適嘅時機進行真正嘅全國大罷工，咁先係大大力錫落政府春袋嘅最佳方法。<br />\n<br />\n堅持黃色經濟圈嘅發展可以令到資本家走向我哋一邊，多一個同路人永遠都唔嫌小。<br />\n<br />\n有投票必須投，要持續翻區議會投票個全民動員嘅模式。<br />\n<br />\n遊行、唱歌、放映等等純和理非活動必須要堅持搞，但要純和理進行，就好似呢幾日嘅集會咁，重新凝聚翻個信念，保持大家對社會現況嘅關注，令運動可以持續哋進行。<br />\n<br />\n和理非嘅活動除咗民眾自發外，都希望來年上任嘅區議員可以一齊搞一齊號召，冇嘢係可以一時三刻完成，要長遠行落去，點解唔試下行一條高級和理非嘅路線呢？<br />\n<br />\n今日美領同尖沙咀見！"},{"pid":"a613c32e8916a88e015b3ce56893d5026f571424","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"小推一下"},{"pid":"d734c2925a09ad3a0a73898ae0b385c0221bb8b6","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:35.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"11036781313b0427eaecc09b8ab9d0736b913fe1","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"33a1e7e48fc0f26447de551c43de0adbf14d82f7","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d702ba6a1a7919f2387240819f38aefb340e32e6","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:51:10.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"7ae8ae2fe29f43689d36918fdd92cdebde1f67d5","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:51:21.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"42626e2066405c755c50bc5486dcfef420e8f72d","tid":1764101,"uid":28645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T23:51:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20191201/s00001/1575135940668/今3遊行獲批-主辦者料和平-警紅隧戒備-消息-倘平靜擬准民陣下周申請\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F1575135940668%2F%E4%BB%8A3%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9-%E4%B8%BB%